enhanced_by.reason: Validating the input dates before comparison ensures that the dates are in the correct format and can be safely processed.
The compareQuarters method relies on the getCalendar method to convert Date objects to Calendar objects, which are then used for comparison.
Both compareQuarters and compareMonths methods perform similar comparisons but at different granularities (quarters vs. months), making them useful for constructing assertions.
Comparing years can provide additional context when asserting the results of quarter comparisons, especially when the years differ.
